info.title: Kanguro Integration API
info.description:
You can download this API documentation [here](/api), for example to [generate a client via OpenAPI tooling](https://editor-next.swagger.io/). 

The Kanguro Integration API provides endpoints for managing pet insurance
processes, including breed lookup, insurance quotes, and policy management.

It is designed for partners looking to integrate Kanguro's insurance
offerings into their platforms. 

This documentation is interactive! You can click on **Authorize** to input your API Key and try it out!

To obtain an API key, [write us](mailto:d.hull@kanguroseguro.com)
